import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground } from 'docz'
import Button from './Button'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic Usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button>Push Me</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button>Push Me</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"types"}}>{`Types`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button type="filled">Push Me</Button>
<Button type="outlined">Push Me</Button>
<Button type="ghost">Push Me</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button type="filled">Push Me</Button>
    <Button type="outlined">Push Me</Button>
    <Button type="ghost">Push Me</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"sizes"}}>{`Sizes`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button size="small">Push Me</Button>
<Button size="default">Push Me</Button>
<Button size="large">Push Me</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button size="small">Push Me</Button>
    <Button size="default">Push Me</Button>
    <Button size="large">Push Me</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"sizes-1"}}>{`Sizes`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button fullWidth>Push Me</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button fullWidth>Push Me</Button>
</Playground></MDXTag>
